</a>        </span>
    <h2>Personal Details</h2>
        <div id="details-other-works" class="see-more inline canwrap">
                <h4 class="inline">Other Works:</h4>
: Wrote an unused draft of <a href="/name/nm1099514?ref_=nm_pdt_wrk1">Philip Pullman</a>'s novel "The Subtle Knife", the sequel to <a href="/title/tt0385752?ref_=nm_pdt_wrk2">The Golden Compass</a> (2007). The project was scrapped and the script unused, after disappointing box office results.        </div>

    
    
            <hr/>
        <div id="details-akas" class="see-more inline canwrap">
            <h4 class="inline">Alternate Names:</h4>
            Hoss Amini
        </div>
    
